title: 276 - Citizen's Arrest
description: In this episode, the conversation about loyalty and being exposed to greatness continues. The guys discuss the core values we all need to ensure success and ET pointed out four factors that change his life. The TIME invested on your craft, the EFFORT put in, the ENERGY provided, & how you EXECUTE the plan are factors that ensure success.
